// Repo-local Go workspace: resolves the example's dependency on the SDK from
// source (./sdk/go) so the monorepo builds and runs without the SDK being
// published. Tooling and CI for the SDK itself run inside sdk/go and ignore
// this; the deploy Dockerfile (built from the example dir alone) does too.
go 1.23

use (
	./examples/go-gameserver
	./sdk/go
)
